====Info==== Application Id : its the discord application id you get from https://discord.com/developers/applications if you don't have one then Create one by clicking new application then enter the name of the application the name of the application is the thing that will show you playing after that copy and paste the id Note: this is now a password so sharing it won't result in anything!
Details : the text under your application name.
Status : the text under your details if available if not then its the text under your application name
Timer : the time showing under your details, status or application name. put 0 to make a count up timer from now put plus and number of seconds to make a count up that starts after the amount of seconds you enter put negative and number of seconds to make a count down
Large Image : the image next to your application name. you can upload an image by going to your application then rich presence then art assets then upload your photo Note: it might take some time to be uploaded to discord, you can refresh and check it if its uploaded or not. put the name of your image the same as the one you upload to your application
Large Image Hint : the text that shows on top your Large Image then you hover over it.
Small Image : the image at the bottom right of your Large Image. you can upload an image by going to your application then rich presence then art assets then upload your photo Note: it might take some time to be uploaded to discord, you can refresh and check it if its uploaded or not. put the name of your image the same as the one you upload to your application
Small Image Hint : the text that shows on top your Small Image then you hover over it.
2 Buttons : these are buttons that is clickable and show at the bottom of the whole rich presence paste a vailed url in button link and put the text of the button on button text.
Clear button : clears every field.
Update button : after you enter everything you can press Update to show your rich presence or to save the fields you entered!
down arrow button : import your program data.
up arrow button : export your program data.
====Changelog==== Version 1.1.2 -new help menu -import & export buttons -better text fields -advance time field
